    <string name="onboarding_title">Authorized Use Only</string>
    <string name="onboarding_body">HexStrike AI is a security research assistant that can run
        network and application security tools (nmap, sqlmap, ffuf, and similar) inside a private
        Linux environment on this device, driven by an AI model you configure.\n\nOnly use it
        against systems you own or are explicitly authorized to test — for example your own
        lab, a CTF target, or an engagement covered by a signed scope of work. Running scans or
        exploitation tools against systems without authorization may be illegal in your
        jurisdiction.\n\nYou are solely responsible for how you use this app.</string>
